{"tid":1328932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(吹水PO)遲遲不出水炮車的原因","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:17:43.000Z","uid":80396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3024af6a37e05efe92493d3f6f80011c502aad0","tid":1328932,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"其實POPO武力，由14年開始我地都見得7788。但由於香港人適應力極強，短短一個月由驚催淚彈變到慢慢淋返熄佢。咩咩速龍都由見到就跑，變到打返轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我覺得點解到今日都未有水炮車<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係萬一出左冇人驚，咁就大獲了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純吹水<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721，大團結</span>"},{"pid":"821817c1e32758375dede650ca47ab16e1b77a5e","tid":1328932,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔信，水炮車咁撚勁<br />\n<br />\n我估怕一出死幾件就真"},{"pid":"bd6f66614336ab164965046a0d9bd6ec9d88e98e","tid":1328932,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"821817c1e32758375dede650ca47ab16e1b77a5e","tid":1328932,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔信，水炮車咁撚勁<br />\n<br />\n我估怕一出死幾件就真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"所以大家吹下水勿認真<br />\n其實水炮車有個痛腳，就係移動唔快，因為下下用都要拖喉。反而推動遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bac564489aff3a5d61820cd96c546e22761be5","tid":1328932,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6f66614336ab164965046a0d9bd6ec9d88e98e","tid":1328932,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"821817c1e32758375dede650ca47ab16e1b77a5e","tid":1328932,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔信，水炮車咁撚勁<br />\n<br />\n我估怕一出死幾件就真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"所以大家吹下水勿認真<br />\n其實水炮車有個痛腳，就係移動唔快，因為下下用都要拖喉。反而推動遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"有機會出呀真係"}]}